Smith predictor closed-loop (theoretical):
  G_cl_smith = C*G*e^(-tau*s) / (1 + C*G)
  Characteristic equation: 1 + C*G = 0 (delay removed from feedback)

Equivalent Smith predictor controller:
  C_eq = C / (1 + C*G*(1 - e^(-tau*s)))

